Privacy Policy for Shayari Hub

Effective Date: 02/09/2024

At Shayari Hub, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle your information when you use our app.

1. No Collection of Personal Information
Our Shayari app does not collect, store, or share any personal information from its users. We respect your privacy and ensure that your use of our
app is completely anonymous.

2. No Use of Third-Party Services
Our app does not use any third-party services that collect or share user data, such as analytics or advertising networks.

3. Security
Since we do not collect any data, there is no personal information to protect. Your privacy is inherently safeguarded by our design.

4. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected in the updated privacy policy available within the app or on our website.

5. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, feel free to contact us at p4programming1@gmail.com.

6. Consent
By using our app, you consent to this Privacy Policy.

